{"tid":2285550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奧巴鹿：：川普至今仍否認敗選 將威脅美國民主","createTime":"2020-11-14T07:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T17:23:18.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f9a13afa54f65bf7413f80fa75ab9fa3f8dbaf","tid":2285550,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T07:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.worldjournal.com/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/wj/paper/2020/11/14/9072713.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;q=75&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.worldjournal.com%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fwj%2Fpaper%2F2020%2F11%2F14%2F9072713.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26q%3D75%26nt%3D1&h=93b2dfa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGetty Images<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前總統歐巴馬(Barack Obama)12日接受哥倫比亞廣播公司(CBS)的訪問，談及川普總統至今仍拒絕承認選舉結果時，形容川普此舉正在威脅美國民主的合法性，且步上一條危險的道路。<br />\n<br />\n歐巴馬告訴CBS主持人佩利(Scott Pelley)表示：「不僅對即將上任的白登政府產生威脅，距離破壞民主的合法性也只有一步之遙。」<br />\n<br />\n儘管目前各大媒體皆宣布白登為總統當選人，白登也即將展開執政團隊的人事規畫，並陸續收到各國元首的賀電，但川普仍堅決否認敗選，且對多州提出選舉訴訟，宣稱這次的選舉充斥舞弊及其他違規的現象。<br />\n<br />\n歐巴馬在訪談中指出，川普拒絕承認選舉結果也凸顯他不認輸的個性，更讓他對其他承認選舉結果的共和黨人感到不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121148/5014799\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2Fwj%2Fstory%2F121148%2F5014799&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=964a91bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121148/5014799</a>"},{"pid":"578c829454ba17c04e90e9bf675c94ba62b27a48","tid":2285550,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500e1d313402d0c54a4fb66674ef1a12d04dc195","tid":2285550,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T16:47:14.000Z","msg":"<